Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------NEXT-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露蒂的内裤是尾巴开口条纹样式的条纹裤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要取奇怪的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做自由研究的作业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.43,0:01:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由研究？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:01:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天学校不是布置了这样的作业了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么  只要是自己感兴趣的就去研究
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定做内裤的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这么说  突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二条内裤  发现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢尔妲是兜裆布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是兜裆布…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三第四条内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔芙和柯是灯笼裤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说这是蕾丝内裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟内裤扯上关系  你就变得和超人一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对内裤可是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内裤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为是学校的作业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱蒂的给我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的可是稍微有点过激哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是内裤？还是绳子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为  为什么那个地方会有金属饰物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎没起到内裤的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内衣？伊妮的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊妮一直穿着外套  没有内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  伊妮是真空的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带点心来了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自重啊  明日叶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我研究大家的内裤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员真空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家都不穿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是休息日  所以内裤也休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一不小心就把内衣全部洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是没办法的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧身裤就是我的内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  尤娜是紧身内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:03:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要作奇怪的省略啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（紧身内裤x1  真空x2  大人的内裤x1  灯笼裤x2  兜裆布x1  条纹裤x1）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是全部了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是热血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然露天浴场很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时间段是我们男人包场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  开放感也是满满的哦  直哉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥拉夫  全都看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么女人一样的话  快全脱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  给我看你的内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸是运动裤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥拉夫是四角裤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉先生居然穿这种内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内裤的研究已经足够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  露蒂做的是什么研究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是露蒂的自由研究？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  龙的蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快要孵化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日叶  公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了  爸爸  奥拉夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋好像没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  巢却…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家没了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样  明明马上就要孵化了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊明日叶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管了  大家都脱掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内裤之家  完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个可是温温的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始孵化了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.47,0:06:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要当个好孩子哦  内裤酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内裤酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那只小龙的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将就吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:07:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  我和露蒂的作业都是内裤的自由研究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
